  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b85\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0b95\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8a\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1 : \u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Inviting employees to government offices : Another circular for a period of one month",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The already issued circular restricting call-up of employees to government offices has been extended for another month.",
        "On June 20, the Ministry of Public Administration and Internal Affairs took a decision to limit the call of government employees to duty in view of the shortage of fuel and inconveniences in transportation facilities.",
        "However, Secretary of the Ministry of General Administration M. M. B. K. Mayatunne also sent a circular to the secretaries of the ministries, the chief secretaries of the provinces and the heads of the departments yesterday, again for a period of one month.",
        "He has also requested that the officers who may come to duty by taking advantage of the said circular should pay attention to the fact that they do not socialize on duty.",
        "Fuel supply measures are being taken to address the fuel crisis in the country. Accordingly, public transport services will gradually return to normal in a few days.",
        "In view of that, the Secretary of the Ministry has also said that this circular letter will not be a hindrance to call the necessary officers to carry out the services for the general public which cannot be done online."
      ],
